\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line Spero Villioti Couture - Fashion Design is  registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training and is accredited to offer a Diploma in Fashion Design by the HEQC . \cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\line \par\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
